{"tid":1818725,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全港精神健康調查顯示　近15%年青人有重度抑鬱","createTime":"2020-01-10T06:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T07:21:32.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"54e2b2fb7d61e8e95c3d2fc5c0daf6e0a7f6ea2d","tid":1818725,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T06:50:09.000Z","msg":"政府委託大學近月進行的全港性精神健康調查，初步數據顯示，本港近一成半年青人診斷為有重度抑鬱症發作，比率是日本、南韓和內地等地年青人，介乎約3至4%的幾倍。<br />\n<br />\n由政府成立的精神健康諮詢委員會，去年起委託兩間大學，展開全港性精神健康調查。委員之一，負責調查社區青年人精神健康部份的港大醫學院精神醫學系系主任陳友凱，在立法會一個委員會表示，在為期三年的研究中，因應近月的社會事件，特別加入觀察，初步數據顯示，在社區抽樣380名年青人當中，14.7%有重度抑鬱症發作 ，當中社會事件所受的壓力、使用手機上網的行為、個人抗逆力和與家人不和，都是重要因素。"},{"pid":"7bdcf5cd4e53ff308646464044a54039e3001610","tid":1818725,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T06:50:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1247152&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1247152%26csid%3D261_341&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdCWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=464e0873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1247152&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"dc2d248ee66e949e9cdc9ad3cc6af2756b15d6f2","tid":1818725,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T06:51:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">上前線舒發<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"30d6bf31c3cc4717faa9ef74526b1af7c0425290","tid":1818725,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T06:54:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"594a226bc6b13854adb467c58075e3930d32ecb5","tid":1818725,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T06:57:00.000Z","msg":"運動頭三個月，我都覺得自己有問題，瞓唔到又會係到偷偷喊！好內疚又無助！"},{"pid":"79b8f3f149f44812ea98fbf3e14f257be722812d","tid":1818725,"uid":321674,"l